programme.desc: Neve Campbell, Fairuza Balk and Robin Tunney star in this teen thriller about four private school misfits who form a coven to summon the dark forces they need to wreak havoc on their persecutors. Having just moved to Los Angeles, Sarah (Tunney) is an outsider at St. Benedict's Academy until she meets three other social outcasts. Nancy (Balk), Bonnie (ampbell) and Rochelle (Rachel True) will never fit in with the "in" crowd. Nancy, Bonnie and Rochelle dabble in the occult, and when they notice Sarah has the powers of a natural witch, they talk her into joining their coven. With the addition of a fourth witch they find they can cast spells they couldn't before, and the teenage witches are suddenly not only able to get the attention, praise and love they have long been denied, but also to exact vengeance on classmates, parents and boyfriends. They learn, however, that everything comes with a price. Support cast includes Skeet Ulrich and Rachel True.

One fateful day, hotel guest and senatorial candidate Christopher Marshall meets Marisa and mistakes her for a wealthy socialite. After an enchanting evening together, the two fall madly in love. Can two people from very different worlds overcome their differences and live happily ever after?

programme.title: Made of Honour

He resolves that when she gets back, he'll ask Hannah to marry him, but his plans go awry when he learns that she has become engaged to a handsome and wealthy Scotsman. When Hannah asks Tom to be her maid of honour, he reluctantly agrees to fill the role, but only so he can attempt to woo Hannah and stop the wedding before it's too late.

programme.desc: Henry lives an enviable life in a Hawaiian paradise, spending every night with a beautiful tourist in search of an island fling. programme.title: Crazy, Stupid, Love.
programme.desc: After his wife Emily's confession that she had a fling with her co-worker David and that she wants a divorce, Cal starts to haunt his local bar, devastated at his situation. He observes a handsome young womaniser, Jacob, in action as he lays slick moves on various young ladies, but is surprised when Jacob notices his incessant sad-sack rantings. Jacob offers to help Cal get back in the dating game, and Cal is astonished when the combination of an image makeover and some smart tips actually work.

programme.title: Rock of Ages

programme.title: Fifty Shades of Grey
programme.desc: This erotic romance charts the masochistic relationship between a sexually inexperienced woman and a steely businessman who harbours painful and long buried secrets from his past.

programme.title: The First Wives Club
programme.desc: Join Diane Keaton, Bette Midler and Goldie Hawn in this sinfully satisfying revenge romp about a trio of first wives who team up to teach their lying, cheating ex-husbands a lesson. Ivana Trump's galvanising cameo - 'don't get mad, dahlinks, get everytink' - sets the scene in a comedy that hinges on the self-mockery of its ageless stars. Midler's ball-busting shtick, Keaton's ditsy vulnerability and Hawn's eternal youth are just light-hearted grist for the mill of female friendship as a serious source of strength.

programme.title: Message in a Bottle
programme.desc: A divorced newspaper researcher finds a love letter in a bottle washed up on a beach and tracks it to a grieving widower.

programme.title: The Mirror Has Two Faces
programme.desc: Rose Morgan, who still lives with her mother, is a professor of Romantic Literature who desperately longs for passion in her life. Gregory Larkin, a mathematics professor, has been burned by passionate relationships and longs for a sexless union based on friendship and respect. They're two people with almost nothing in common, but fate in the form of a personal ad and a meddling sister brings them together. And without physical attraction to complicate matters, Rose and Greg become best friends and soon agree to an unconventional marriage built on intellectual passion instead of sexual heat. But when two people meet, marry, try to remain celibate and then fall in love they realise they are courting chaos.
